      "beast_baseline": "thanks. i checked the ALB idle timeout and it's set to 60s which should be fine since our traffic is pretty constant. i also looked at the security groups and they seem tight, nothing stands out there. \n\nif it's not the timeout, what else could cause that errno 104? could it be something happening at the OS level or maybe a weird network hiccup in the VPC?",
