      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i'll dig into dmesg. but its just so random. like there's no pattern at all to when it hits. one minute everything is fine, then boom, a reset. it almost feels like something is just randomly messing with the packets or dropping them for no reason. \n\nany idea if there's any weird edge case in the VPC peering or something that would cause that kind of erratic behavior?",
